content.task: Validate CI pipeline fixes and provide comprehensive status report on all three pipelines (Main CI, Production Deployment, CI Health Dashboard)
content.context: We have implemented comprehensive fixes: 1) Fixed requirements-dev.txt version conflicts causing Production Deployment failures, 2) Identified test timeout issues (only with full suite), 3) Verified multi-agent system operational via MCP, 4) Confirmed hard compliance enforcement active. Need validation that all CI pipelines are now operational.
